loadngLibDestAddressSetIndex OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Integer32 (0..65535) MAX-ACCESS not-accessible STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The index for this table. Necessary because multiple addresses may be associated with a given loadngIfIndex." REFERENCE "RFC XXXX - The Lightweight On-demand Ad hoc Distance-vector Routing Protocol - Next Generation (LOADng), Clausen, T., Colin de Verdiere, A., Yi, J., Niktash, A., Igarashi, Y., Satoh, H., Herberg, U., Lavenu, C., Lys, T., C. Perkins, and J. Dean, January 2013" ::= { loadngLibDestAddressSetEntry 1 }
